Installation

Create a virtual environment
python3 -m venv .venv

Activate it
source .venv/bin/activate

Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

Running the App

To open the UI:
python3 scripts/run_gui.py

To run only the background Chrome monitor in the terminal:
python3 scripts/run_monitor_only.py

Configuration

The following environment variables can override defaults from config.py:

CHROME_GUARD_CHROME_PATH

CHROME_GUARD_CPU_TOTAL

CHROME_GUARD_CPU_SINGLE

CHROME_GUARD_POLL_INTERVAL

CHROME_GUARD_SUSTAINED_HITS
